<div id="new_list">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-8">
      <h3>New List</h3>
      <%= form_for @list do |f| %>
    		<div class="form-group">
          <%= f.label :title %>
          <%= f.text_field :title, class: "form-control input-lg", placeholder: "Title" %>
        </div>

    		<div class="form-group">
          <%= f.label :description, "Description (optional)" %>
          <%= f.text_area :description, class: "form-control input-lg", placeholder: "Description" %>
        </div>

        <div id="list" class="form-group">
          <ul>
            <li><input class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Item 1" type="text" name="list[item]" id="list_item_1" /></li>
            <li><input class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Item 2" type="text" name="list[item]" id="list_item_2" /></li>
            <li><input class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Item 3" type="text" name="list[item]" id="list_item_3" /></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <%# f.fields_for :items do |item| %>
          <%#= item.text_field :body, class: "form-control input-lg", placeholder: "List Item" %>
          <%#= item.hidden_field :position, value: 1, class: "form-control input-lg", placeholder: "Item" %>
        <%# end %>

        <div class="row settings">
          <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div id="bullets" class="type selected">
              <%#= f.radio_button :ordered, false, checked: true %>
              <ul><li>Bullets</li></ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div id="numbers" class="type">
              <%#= f.radio_button :ordered, true %>
              <ol><li>Numbers</li></ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%= f.hidden_field :user_id, value: 1 %>
        <%= f.submit "LIST IT", :class => "btn btn-lg btn-listyourlist btn-block" %>

      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 hints">
      <h3>Helpful Hints?</h3>
      <p>Drinking vinegar lo-fi Brooklyn, Carles Shoreditch mlkshk forage Helvetica. Try-hard small batch street art High Life, dreamcatcher next level plaid narwhal Schlitz semiotics 90's kitsch selfies.</p>
      <p>Master cleanse typewriter roof party, hella distillery single-origin coffee blog chambray. McSweeney's occupy single-origin coffee Blue Bottle, asymmetrical cornhole try-hard raw denim Pitchfork butcher irony deep v tote bag actually disrupt. Beard freegan Echo Park Intelligentsia yr. Williamsburg Wes Anderson ugh Pitchfork 3 wolf moon, vegan try-hard stumptown kitsch Vice Godard.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
